title: Astroburger
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Burgers and fries, and Greek food in an American diner setting. Has a separate vegetarian menu offering burgers with Gardenburger brand soy protein patty, vegan ribs, soy cheese, and non-dairy milk options. Fresh orange and apple juice available. Veg food is cooked on separate grills and woks. Has drive-thru.
